__data__.text:
assistant: Move to the kitchen area
Scan the kitchen floor for misplaced items
Identify a misplaced toaster on the kitchen floor
Pick up the toaster
Move to the kitchen counter
Place the toaster in the toaster slot near the kitchen sink
Scan the kitchen counter for misplaced items
Identify a misplaced bowl on the kitchen counter
Pick up the bowl
Move to the cabinet near the refrigerator
Open the cabinet door
Place the bowl on the middle shelf of the cabinet
Close the cabinet door
Scan the kitchen table for misplaced items
Identify a misplaced knife on the kitchen table
Pick up the knife
Move to the drawer near the kitchen sink
Open the drawer
Place the knife in the knife holder inside the drawer
Close the drawer
Scan the kitchen area for any remaining misplaced items
Identify a misplaced broom on the kitchen floor
Pick up the broom
Move to the broom closet
Open the broom closet door
Place the broom inside the broom closet
Close the broom closet door
Scan the kitchen area again to confirm all items are in their standard storage locations
